name: The Last Time We Were Young

metadata.name: The Last Time We Were Young #1
metadata.description:
Summer, 1978. 

Grand Canyon National Park, Arizona, USA

Taken w/ a Yashica Electro 35 GSN Rangefinder on Kodachrome Film.

When was the last time you felt free? It's 1978, and we're spending the summer roaming the United States together. We've got a sense of wonder, we've got a camera, and we've got each other. 

This is the last time we were young.
